    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "Step 5B: Troubleshoot and Reload Model\n",
        "What this does:\n",
        "We'll clear the model from memory and reload it, this time using a more reliable PEGASUS checkpoint. We'll use google/pegasus-xsum which is very stable.\n",
        "Why it's necessary:\n",
        "The garbled output indicates the model weights may not have loaded correctly. Let's start fresh with a different checkpoint."
