        "Step 11: Fine-tuning PEGASUS on Custom DataWhat this does:\n",
        "We'll fine-tune PEGASUS on a small custom dataset. This demonstrates how to adapt the pre-trained model to your specific domain or style of summarization.Why it's necessary:\n",
        "While PEGASUS works well out-of-the-box, fine-tuning on domain-specific data (medical, legal, scientific) can significantly improve performance for specialized use cases."
      ],
